comments.author: royalfestus
comments.body: There are many new announcement threads in the forum for this year, but I notice insufficient information and new moderators. The new member's status is not an issue but the trust in the new member to announce a new project and availability for the project in the forum. It should include links to the social platform and information about the team behind the project which are used to identify the team. In order to make announcement threads more appealing and interesting, the OP should engage some people to prepare them. The service is not free, however
